{
  "texts": [
    "The selected variants were deemed feasible to assess with publicly available information, and each response was agreed upon by two members.",
    "This data reports characteristics of selected variants that are essential to determining therapeutic eligibility, including the variant's pathomechanism, haploinsufficiency status of the gene it affects, inheritance pattern of associated diseases, splicing effects, and findings from prior therapeutic approaches explored.",
    "We manually reformatted this data into 47 questionanswer examples.",
    "Genetic variants are specified in HGVS notation.",
    "Questions were preceded with a few sentences of context containing some details on what types of evidence are preferred and proper answer format."
